ault-executor-6471\" java.lang.Error: Injected error\"` 出现1456次。\n\n2. **组件: frontend**\n   - **原因**: `failed to retrieve ads` 和 `rpc error: code = Unknown desc =` 等错误不断出现，可能由于 adservice 的错误影响到 frontend 服务无法正常从 adservice 中获取广告。\n   - **证据**: `\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = \"` 出现多次，影响多个 frontend 的实例。\n\n### 输出格式\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"rpc error\", \"Unknown desc\", \"failed to retrieve ads\", \"Exception\", \"Error\", \"failed to start\", \"InvocationTargetException\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Injected error noted in Java thread leading to service fault\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Exception in thread \\\"grpc-default-executor-6471\\\" java.lang.Error: Injected error\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Failed to retrieve ads possibly due to adservice being non-functional\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unknown desc =\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此分析表明系统故障可能由 adservice 中的异常处理不当以及影响到 frontend 的广告检索而导致。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据获取的数据，我对指标进行了分析。以下是异常调用链和显著变化的指标：\n\n### 异常指标扫描:\n\n1. **Node 级别异常**:\n   - `aiops-k8s-05`: \n     - `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 减少，median_change_ratio: 0.3125\n     - `node_memory_usage_rate` 增加，median_change_ratio: 0.2982\n\n2. **Pod 和 Service 级别异常**:\n   - `emailservice-0`:\n     - `rrt_max` 增加显著，p99_change_ratio: 1.3344\n   - `currencyservice-0`:\n     - `rrt_max` 增加显著，p99_change_ratio: 1.2894 \n   - `adservice-0`:\n     - `pod_cpu_usage` 有明显变化，p99_change_ratio: 1.5736\n\n3. **内存相关 Pod 异常**:\n   - `redis-cart-0`:\n     - 所在 Node `aiops-k8s-08` 显示内存可用量减少但Pod整体资源使用正常\n\n### 异常归因\n- **Node 自身异常 (aiops-k8s-05)**: `node_memory_usage_rate` 增加显著，且无明显Pod归因\n- **Pod 性能问题 (emailservice-0, currencyservice-0, adservice-0)**: `rrt_max` 和 `pod_cpu_usage` 指标显示高资源使用\n\n### 相关指标名称\n```json\n{\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 初步假设\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-05\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_usage_rate 增加且 node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes 减少，可能是系统内存不足或泄漏。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate median_change_ratio: 0.2982\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 中位数变化显著，指示服务延迟剧增。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max p99_change_ratio: 1.3344\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 中位数变化显著，指示服务延迟剧增。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max p99_change_ratio: 1.2894\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage 变化显著，表明pod可能存在资源争用问题。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage p99_change_ratio: 1.5736\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n以上信息将在后续阶段进行更多分析以判断具体错误来源。"}
